attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Premier Realty Lake Minnetonka

data.description: Amazing opportunity to own a spacious five bedroom home with wonderful, treed & playable yard. Never before on the market, this single owner home features a kitchen with hardwood floors, a double wall oven & helpful informal dining area. There is a great formal dining room, with access to the deck. Notice all the lovely sunshine & SO MUCH space in the living room. The primary bedroom has generous closets & a private bathroom. Making the house flexible and a great investment, upper level has two additional bedrooms & a full bathroom. The lower level sports a fantastic family room with plenty of space for hobbies, relaxing and playing – including a wet bar. There’s a convenient, dedicated office space, plus two additional bedrooms & another bathroom in the lower level. Check out the backyard & think of all the fun you could have here. Great bones here (new roof 2023 & updated electrical panel 2019). Build equity! Easy commute, trails nearby, minutes to Ridgedale & surrounding amenities.
